snippet.title: Molecats is now available on Steam Early Access
snippet.description:
Molecats is an indirect-control puzzle adventure ...with traps!

http://store.steampowered.com/app/338290/Molecats/

The goal is to lead Molecats through the levels, divided into Tiles. Molecats cannot be controlled directly, but they still respond to some tricky commands. And, of course, the Tiles themselves can be manipulated: rotated, flipped or slided.

Sticky traps, shiny secrets, strange creatures and tasty mushrooms await!

http://www.molecats.com
